summary: My Mimikyu and Pikachu, Mochi and Anpan, are best friends, which is great- I was initially worried that they might not get...
question: My Mimikyu and Pikachu, Mochi and Anpan, are best friends, which is great- I was initially worried that they might not get along. The one problem is, though, Mochi has latched onto Anpan so much that she gets very anxious without him. So when I take Anpan outside on sunny days or do anything else with him that she can't or doesn't want to join him for, she just cries and cries (read: shrieks.) Do you have any advice on how to help her adjust?
answer: Do some things to build up her confidence. Training, walking, playing. You can also to try and give her more affection so she won’t depend so much on Anpan. See if this will work.
